description: Downloads your tax documents to the Amazon S3 bucket that you specify in your request.

parameters.name: destinationS3Location
parameters.description: The Amazon S3 bucket that you specify to download your tax documents to. The name of your Amazon S3 bucket that you specify to download your tax documents to. prefix (string) --- The Amazon S3 object prefix that you specify for your tax document file.

nested_params.name: bucket
nested_params.description: The name of your Amazon S3 bucket that you specify to download your tax documents to.

nested_params.name: prefix
nested_params.description: The Amazon S3 object prefix that you specify for your tax document file.

parameters.name: taxDocumentMetadata
parameters.description: The metadata for your tax document. The tax document access token, which contains information that the Tax Settings API uses to locate the tax document. The name of your tax document.

nested_params.name: taxDocumentAccessToken
nested_params.description: The tax document access token, which contains information that the Tax Settings API uses to locate the tax document.

nested_params.name: taxDocumentName
nested_params.description: The name of your tax document.

nested_items.name: destinationFilePath
nested_items.description: The file path of the Amazon S3 bucket where you want to download your tax document to.

nested_items.name: presignedS3Url
nested_items.description: The Amazon S3 presigned URL of the tax registration document.
